<span style='float: right; width: 280px; height: 187px; margin: 0 0 5px 5px; border: 1px solid black;'><script type='text/javascript'>flash_object ('http://graphics.millsberry.com/buddy/buddy_featured.swf', '280', '187', 'userName=jollii&buddyTimeStamp=20051010&buddyScriptURL=http%3A%2F%2Fmillsberry.com%2Fbuddy%2Fprocess_buddy.phtml&unixTimeStamp=1193060002&serverTimeOffset=28800', '', 'exactfit', 'transparent');</script></span>
Meet <b>Jollii</b>, our citizen of the week!<br><br>Jollii lives at <a href='/home/?user=jollii'>32016 Breeze Street</a>, in the rolling farmland of Golden Valley.  She has been enjoying life in Millsberry since May 5, 2005.<br><br>When she first moved to Millsberry, Jollii was very shy.   In the few short months that she's been here, however, Jollii has gained a lot of confidence and now has a much easier time meeting people.  One of the ways that Jollii went about making friends was by signing up for a number of after-school activities at <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/academy/">Millsberry Academy</a>, allowing her to quickly meet lots of people with similar interests and hobbies.  To this day, she still spends a good part of her afternoons at the Academy, arranging a bake sale for one of the many clubs she's in, painting scenery for the school play, or helping out at the <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/shop.phtml?shop_id=10">Student Store</a>.<br><br>One of Jollii's favorite after-school activities is putting together and performing musical shows with her friends.  Despite her shyness, Jollii is able to really come alive onstage.  She is a very good singer, so her friends often choose her for the lead role in their shows.  Even though she seems quite confident while strutting around the stage in her black, dark blue, and pink costumes, Jollii is actually very modest, and always makes sure that her costars are having a great time too.<br><br>Jollii loves music, so it's no surprise that she and her friends enjoy writing their own songs for their musical shows.  Jollii's songs are especially unique because they're an interesting combination of her three favorite musical styles:  new age, rap, and world music.  Jollii recently decided to record some of the best pieces she's written, and headed down to the <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/studio/">Millsberry Recording Studio</a> right away.  Because fans of her stage performances were so excited to have their very own recording of Jollii's songs, one of her tracks quickly rose to the top of the Cinnamon Toast Crunch Top Ten chart!<br><br>In her spare time, Jollii likes to catch movies at the <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/complex/">Downtown Entertainment Complex</a> with her friends.  Though musicals have a special place in her heart, Jollii likes all types of movies.  She can also often be found spending the afternoon at her best friend's house, where they do homework, write new songs together, or even design costumes for their latest show.<br><br>Thanks for being a fine citizen, Jollii, and congratulations on being named Millsberry's citizen of the week!</div>
